{"tid":1717340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塞半條路係咪有用過塞晒成條路","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:33:59.000Z","uid":234509,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83c1506c3d74bcd2510cf57de761ed5678b54d9f","tid":1717340,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"塞半條路可以搞到得番一條行車線<br />\n得一條行車線嘅時候車速就會減慢<br />\n而班港豬永遠覺得唔會影響到佢地就唔會理<br />\n所以唔會特登落車去清RB<br />\n<br />\n而塞成條路嘅話<br />\n班港豬見到過唔到<br />\n就個個都落晒車秒清rb<br />\n根本唔會有太大作用"},{"pid":"506b92f12682fc57a70558b44bacfddfbabd62df","tid":1717340,"uid":35348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"c0334c5135a5c90282b265cd66a037d684724358","tid":1717340,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"仲要整到條路有咁難行得咁難行 要佢地 兜黎兜去避RB"},{"pid":"c41850537b3347771c94e6489f4867e3ee567a7e","tid":1717340,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"aggar"},{"pid":"a4d414ebd89719aac6c0ea995fef76118bb76bcc","tid":1717340,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b270cc03ded8e8510095982b23daaf2dfdc36a","tid":1717340,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好玩隧道口，尤其不斷加價當你地市民死既果條隧道"},{"pid":"d6ba19713d0b8582a6f29ad0c8d433f62cc4fc42","tid":1717340,"uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"左邊係巴士停車位，建議塞右邊。<br />\n一次只能容納一部巴士停低上落車，其他所有車要慢慢排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都有人話過因為左邊係巴士上落車位所以要塞左邊，塞右邊都係會搞到啲人忍唔住拆rb<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13b9c66e0ced3de1b7b7749eb98bf8614091043","tid":1717340,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"架車有得郁下，佢哋就絕對唔會落車搬，因為一有位就可能會俾其他車攝又或者俾後面bu <br />\n<br />\n所以路障唔好下下封死<br />\n<br />\n前線手足真係應該參考下"},{"pid":"b82554fc748edc78e4426f2407272ff3a82c8b27","tid":1717340,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"dbfa2ccf1efade5ea7bd7d2ace3e085527f3fb86","tid":1717340,"uid":115965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"seems可行"}]}